goal_text = "\"Everything is working splendidly, only...\" The fat man fidgets, wiggling in his seat.

\"Yes, Mr. Rutherford?\"

\"Janice made the best coffee, you see, black gold, it was!\" Rutherford lick his lips, gaze drifting away dreamily. \"If your machines can do the same, on top of what you've managed so far, you'll have my full support!\"

\"I will see what we can manage.\""
